title: Last Man [v0.52, Eng/Ru] - erotic quest with RPG elements
description:
Story: After global epidemic, every man on Earth died except you.

You should investigate the cause of what happened, why it has not affected your character and try to adapt and survive in the new world. And of course meet many single women.

All of your decisions and actions during the game will affect future events.

Changes:
- more story
- new day added
- new locations
- new date with Dasha
- new scene in Casino
- bug fixes


More info: vortexcannon.ru
